## 7. API 명세 (권장)

### 7.1 Profile
- `GET /meeting/profile/me`
- `POST /meeting/profile`
- `PUT /meeting/profile`
- `POST /meeting/profile/photos`
- `DELETE /meeting/profile/photos/:photoId`

### 7.2 Recommendation
- `GET /meeting/recommendations?cursor=...`
- `POST /meeting/actions/like`
- `POST /meeting/actions/pass`
- `POST /meeting/actions/block`

### 7.3 Match / Chat
- `GET /meeting/matches`
- `GET /meeting/matches/:matchId/messages?cursor=...`
- `POST /meeting/matches/:matchId/messages`
- `POST /meeting/matches/:matchId/read`
- `POST /meeting/matches/:matchId/leave`

### 7.4 Safety
- `POST /meeting/reports`
- `POST /meeting/blocks`
- `DELETE /meeting/blocks/:targetUserId`

### 7.5 예시 응답
`POST /meeting/actions/like`

```json
{
  "matched": true,
  "matchId": "a2a2f5c0-...",
  "compatibility": {
    "score": 87,
    "band": "GOOD",
    "summary": "오행 균형과 일간 상성이 좋은 편입니다."
  }
}
```

